Compile and Run Java Program in Notepad++

Prerequisite:Java (JRE) must be installed on your system.
How to Check: open cmd and type : java -version    hit enter

if there is no java installed or older one please update it.
	go to Controll Pannel and unistall older one
Link for letest - https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/javase-jdk16-downloads.html#license-lightbox

Step1: Download Notepad++ and install it.
	link- https://github.com/notepad-plus-plus/notepad-plus-plus/releases/download/v7.9.5/npp.7.9.5.Installer.exe

Step2: plugin installation in notepad++

go to notepad++ interface > Plugins > Plugins Admin  search for NppExec  click on  install 
internet connection must be enabled

Step3: java path setup in enviroment variable.

Step4: create java program in notepad++ and run it.
